Steps to follow:
------------------------------------------------------------------
Step 1: Install the Qflow Tool Chain. The VSD team has provided a script to install Qflow and all its dependencies. Visit https://github.com/kunalg123/vsdflow
Step 2: Download and install the EmPowerSoC debian package. 
        To install the package, Open terminal and change directory to the location where the package is downloaded and run the following command:
        sudo gdebi empowersoc-v1.0.deb
        Or, You can install the package using GUI installer.
------------------------------------------------------------------

Requirements:
------------------------------------------------------------------
1) Linux Operating System(preferably Ubuntu)
2) Qflow Tool Chain
3) Python3 and PyQt5
4) Perl
------------------------------------------------------------------
